Class RemoteDocumentProxyImpl

java.lang.Object
  ch.iserver.ace.net.core.RemoteDocumentProxyImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
RemoteDocumentProxyExt, RemoteDocumentProxy
public class RemoteDocumentProxyImpl
extends Object
implements RemoteDocumentProxyExt

Default implementation of type RemoteDocumentProxy.

This class represents the client view of a published, shared document from another user.

See Also:
